  "contentPages" : [ "To read this codex, use your ^orange;Personal Tricorder^reset; and click the Book icon." ],

   "longContentPages" : [
"Welcome customer to the 3rd edition brochure of [REDACTED]'s medical station technologies, detailing all the possible ^yellow;Enhancements^reset; that our medical personnel can bestow upon you.
As our staff will confirm, all procedures and fees are final, refunds are not available. For your safety, these modifications will not persist through a respawn chamber.
^red;Berserker Rage^reset;: 25% More Power, Increased Movement Speed. -50% Knockback Resistance, -35 Protection.
^gray;Glass Cannon^reset;: 100% More Damage at the cost of 90% Less Protection
^green;Immunization^reset;: Provides immunity to most negative status effects. 10% Less Power and Protection.
^white;Juggernaut^reset;: You become immune to knockback and gain 50 protection, but your movement speed is reduced by 33%.
^green;Toxic Cloud^reset;: Every 3 seconds a toxic cloud that lasts 5 seconds and deals 30 piercing damage is released at your location. Every time this happens, you take 5 piercing damage. 20% Increased Hunger Drain.
^#B200FF;Experiment #322^reset;: Applies random positive and/or negative statuses every 10 seconds which last 15-25 seconds.
^red;Trollblood^reset;: Regenerate 40% of damage taken over 5 seconds, at the cost of 20% Less HP and 50% increased Energy Block Time.
^green;Renergizer^reset;: 50% More Energy, 33% More Energy Regeneration. Hunger Drain increased by 25%. 100% Increased Energy Block Time.
^yellow;Hypopanic^reset;: 33% More Energy Regen, -50 Energy. In addition, Increased movement speed the less energy you have (up to +67% speed at 35% energy remaining). Taking damage briefly stops energy regen, and  consumes energy for 150% of damage.
^green;Hivemind^reset;: Shoots a projectile at the closest enemy in a medium radius with a clear line of fire every second, dealing 2.5% of your Max HP as base damage (^orange;affected by power multiplier^reset;) on impact. Drains 0.5% of your Current Health every 0.5 seconds as long as you have more than 10%.
^cyan;Mitochondria^reset;: Consumes 2 energy to regenerate 1 health every 0.15 seconds. Energy will regenerate only at full health.
^#7A7D81;Shadow Repel^reset;: Increases shadow resistance by 50% and grants immunity to shadow status effects, but reduces the overall effectiveness of other resistances (except physical) by 33%.
^#C5B00A;Radiation Repel^reset;: Increases radiation resistance by 50% and grants immunity to radiation status effects, but reduces the overall effectiveness of other resistances (except physical) by 33%.
^#69B115;Poison Repel^reset;: Increases poison resistance by 50% and grants immunity to poison status effects, but reduces the overall effectiveness of other resistances (except physical) by 33%.
^#A1F1FE;Ice Repel^reset;: Increases ice resistance by 50% and grants immunity to ice status effects, but reduces the overall effectiveness of other resistances (except physical) by 33%.
^#E99400;Fire Repel^reset;: Increases fire resistance by 50% and grants immunity to fire status effects, but reduces the overall effectiveness of other resistances (except physical) by 33%.
^#9711E4;Electrical Repel^reset;: Increases electric resistance by 50% and grants immunity to electric status effects, but reduces the overall effectiveness of other resistances (except physical) by 33%.
^#6062EB;Cosmic Repel^reset;: Increases cosmic resistance by 50% and grants immunity to cosmic status effects, but reduces the overall effectiveness of other resistances (except physical) by 33%."
   ],

